xampp

Allow executing file as program
	chmod +x xampp-linux-x64-7.4.6-0-installer.run
	
Disallow executing file as program
		chmod -x xampp-linux-x64-7.4.6-0-installer.run

Install
	sudo ./xampp-linux-x64-7.4.6-0-installer.run
	
Start
	sudo /opt/lampp/xampp start (OR) sudo /opt/lampp/lampp start
	
Stop
	sudo /opt/lampp/xampp stop (OR) sudo /opt/lampp/lampp stop
	
Launch cPanel
	sudo /opt/lampp/manager-linux-x64.run
	
Uninstall
	sudo rm -rf /opt/lampp (OR) sudo /opt/lampp uninstall